						<div class="postbody">It's a modern digital art style inspired by old pixel art, with loose restrictions.<br /><br />This is basically how &quot;normal people&quot; define it knowingly or not, and since it's vague by definition it's pointless to try defining the term on the basis of old computer technical specs al gusto (I know this is Nesdev but still).</div>

					
