					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I have more of a pet peeve with people who call every chip in a system a &quot;processor&quot; as if you can't just make circuitry that does it's specific job by itself and has to execute code.  Nowadays pretty much every chip is a processor of some kind, but back in the 80s and 90s, that wasn't the case.</div>

